-   Have working knowledge of at least one of the following: react.js, Python, MatLab, Java, C++, sql, TensorFlow, Azure
-   Enjoy understanding and solving complex problems
-   Want to pursue a meaningful vision related to the greatest challenge of our time
-   Are a team-player who wants to bring out the best in your colleagues
-   Enjoy working with a high degree of both freedom and responsibility
-   Have experience with writing robust code with focus on re-usability and documentation
-   Knowledge of or interest in power distribution systems, smart grid or renewable energy

**We can offer**

-   A chance to work with cutting-edge smart grid technology
-   Working with a tight-knit and diverse group of highly motivated and skilled people
-   Competitive compensation and great offices, centrally located at StartupLab in Oslo Science Park (Forskningsparken) by Blinderen.
-   Participation in a fun and challenging summer program

