-   You have an attractive academic record to show to.
-   You are passionate about product development
-   You have a solid understanding of computer science fundamentals and software engineering
-   You have some experience with multiple programming languages
-   You possess creative problem-solving skills and excellent troubleshooting skills
-   You are comfortable with working in teams
