performing      
 Keep your eyes and ears open for ways we can further streamline our
development process    

**How you will be doing this**     
 You experiment, test, try, fail and learn all the time – with one thing at a
time    
 You’ll become part of an agile, multidisciplinary team that value active
discussions to help and support each other    
