we are expanding our business    
 Autonomy and respect from day one      
 No regulations or hierarchy, just a lot of interesting and challenging
work to get done. We all wear lots of hats and you will too    
 Room for you to do things your way    
 Competitive compensation and benefits    
 Relaxed and flexible working environment     

**Please send your application to intern@oliasoft.com today. We are eager to hear
from you. We will review applications continuously.**', '2019-02-13 20:16:13+00', '2019-04-15 21:59:00+00', false, NULL, '', '', 'SUMMER_INTERNSHIP', false, false);

