### Position Qualifications

We want engaged students, who can identify themselves with our values and standards. It is important to us that you fit well into the organisation and work environment.  
  
**We are looking for candidates with as many as possible of the following qualities:**

-   Quick learner and data smart
-   Open-minded and curious
-   Self-driven and willing to share
-   Flexible and service-minded
-   Structured and systematic
-   Analytical
-   Able to work both individually and in teams
