Our next big goal is to take Kyte from cabin fields to densely populated areas, and we are looking for talented engineers to take our productivity and customer experience to the next level. Depending on your strengths, you will build the customer-facing app and internal tooling, such as the operations management system and ground control software. We are looking for resourceful students who are comfortable with responsibility!

