-   A truly diverse environment with colleagues from different nationalities

-   Competitive pay and benefits, including pension and insurance
-   Top-notch location at Lysaker/ in Trondheim, close to public transportation

-   Opportunity to work from home when needed
-   Fun and development opportunities - regular social events and monthly hack-days
-   Working with the best of the best makes Disruptive Technologies an excellent place for learning and development, also outside your area of specialization.

  

#### Apply today!
Please submit your CV and include a short cover letter and we will get back to you shortly.
