We offer trial periods of 6-8 weeks, where you decide your own workload. The trial is a test both ways to see if we are a fit. If so, we will hire you as soon as we have a reliable revenue stream. We are also open to offering our first employees a share of stocks at a low price.

**Responsibility areas:**

