- Participate in the entire software development lifecycle, from concept to deployment.
- Contribute to planning and implementing the roadmap.

**Who are you:**

- You have knowledge in TypeScript, Node, TRPC, and REST APIs, with an interest in learning other programming languages and technologies as needes
- You have some experience with full-stack development.

OR

- You have strong understanding of UI/UX principles and ability to design user-friendly solutions
- Some experience in TailwindCSS and SHADCN

AND

- You are independent, collaborative, and eager to learn, with some experience in development environments and higher education.
- You have the ability to work independently as well as part of a team.
- You thrive in an environment with a high degree of freedom and flexibility.

**Benefits of this position:**

