- You get your own desk at our office with 24/7 access (the startup is located at NTNU Gløshaugen in Trondheim).
- Free coffee!
- You get the opportunity to join a promising startup early.
- Opportunities for ownership and stock options in the company.

**Contact info:**

If this sounds exciting, please send an email to Finn Lippestad (finn@equafish.com) and write "I am interested", and we will arrange an interview as soon as it suits you.', '2024-09-09 12:37:00+00', '2024-12-31 22:59:00+00', false, '2024-12-31 22:59:00+00', '', 'finn@equafish.com', 'PARTTIME', false, false);

