-   Embedded Systems / Real-Time Programming
-   Wireless Communication
-   Machine Learning / Signal Processing / Data Science
-   BigData processing
-   Fullstack Cloud development
-   Secure protocols and cryptography
-   DevOps / Cloud infrastructure

  

**Why you will love Disruptive Technologies**

[“Sense the real world everywhere, deliver insights anywhere”](https://www.disruptive-technologies.com/career)

Disruptive Technologies is the award-winning developer of the world’s tiniest, zero-hassle wireless IoT sensors. Our HQ is at Lysaker, Norway and we have global ambitions. We love innovation, and we are here to make the world a greener and better place. Our technology enables sustainable and healthy buildings, efficient operations, superior workplace experiences as well as safe and efficient engineering and refrigeration services. From wellbeing to predictive maintenance and to energy savings, we are connecting people and information to deliver Connected Change™.

You will join a team full of enthusiasm, pride, and relentless energy, surrounded by the fun-loving and open culture of our native Northern Europe. We empower our people, we love working together and we always strive to make the complex simple in order to satisfy our customers.

  

**Your strength and preferences**

